GET http://localhost:8000/payroll-execution/termination-benefits?status=pending
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}

###
# 10) Get single termination/resignation benefit by id (set `{{TERMINATION_BENEFIT_ID}}` above)
